title: São Miguel Bus - AutoViação Micaelense/Varela/CRP

creator: Sousa
descriptionHtml:
In this app, you can have access to the São Miguel Island Bus Schedule.
Check at what time a bus stops at Bus Stops all around the Island.
All the information on this app was found on the bus companies' websites.
If you notice some wrong times in the app please contact me via email.

Notes:
- This app is free. It is optimized for smartphones.
- Compatibility is guaranteed with Tablet devices, although the graphic structure of the app may undergo some changes
- This app has ads to support the creator without any cost.
- You can ‘Support the Creator’ via the links from the app’s “INFO” tab.
- The app, just like the ads, is suitable for all ages.

For the future:
- Multi-Bus Trips Support.
- Map of the island with all bus stops properly identified.
- Price information of the Bus Trip.

If you find any problem or wrong times please report it by email.
sousadev@yahoo.com
- Current information as of September 14, 2021.
